opkg install frr frr-bgpd frr-libfrr frr-staticd frr-vtysh frr-watchfrr frr-zebra

### commands

/etc/init.d/frr restart

### debugging

from cilium-agent:

tcpdump -n -i any tcp port 179

from openwrt:

logread

vtysh
> show ip bgp summary
> show ip bgp
> show ip bgp neighbors
> show ip route
> show ip route bgp